Signed-off-by: Gerd Hoffmann <kraxel@redhat.com>
Acked-by: Sam Ravnborg <sam@ravnborg.org>
Link: http://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20200313084152.2734-1-kraxel@redhat.com
